<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Her Desk Co. — Remote Back-Office Support</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400;1,500&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
:root{
  --cream:#FAF7F2;--white:#FFFFFF;--charcoal:#1C1A16;--gold:#C9A96E;
  --gold-light:#E8D5B0;--gold-pale:#FDF6E8;--grey:#7A7570;
  --border:#E8E2D9;--shadow:rgba(28,26,22,0.07);
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{background:var(--cream);color:var(--charcoal);font-family:"DM Sans",sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;overflow-x:hidden;}
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:5px;}
::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--cream);}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--gold-light);border-radius:3px;}
nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;padding:0 64px;height:68px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;transition:background 0.4s,box-shadow 0.4s;}
nav.scrolled{background:rgba(250,247,242,0.95);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);box-shadow:0 1px 0 var(--border);}
.nav-logo{font-family:"Cormorant Garamond",serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:500;color:var(--charcoal);text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.5px;}
.nav-logo span{color:var(--gold);}
.nav-links{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:32px;list-style:none;}
.nav-links a{font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--charcoal);text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.5px;transition:color 0.2s;}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--gold);}
.nav-cta{background:var(--charcoal);color:var(--cream) !important;padding:9px 20px;border-radius:2px;font-size:11px !important;font-weight:600 !important;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;transition:background 0.2s !important;}
.nav-cta:hover{background:var(--gold) !important;color:var(--charcoal) !important;}
.hero{min-height:100vh;background:var(--cream);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:100px 64px 80px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.hero-ring-1{position:absolute;right:60px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);width:360px;height:360px;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.15);pointer-events:none;}
.hero-ring-2{position:absolute;right:110px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);width:220px;height:220px;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.08);pointer-events:none;}
.hero-dot-a{position:absolute;right:248px;top:34%;width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);opacity:0.45;}
.hero-dot-b{position:absolute;left:64px;bottom:28%;width:3px;height:3px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);opacity:0.25;}
.hero-content{max-width:1160px;margin:0 auto;width:100%;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 400px;gap:80px;align-items:center;position:relative;z-index:2;}
.hero-left{animation:fadeUp 0.8s ease both;}
.eyebrow{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:3.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:22px;}
.eyebrow::before{content:"";width:24px;height:1px;background:var(--gold);}
h1{font-family:"Cormorant Garamond",serif;font-size:54px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.1;color:var(--charcoal);margin-bottom:22px;letter-spacing:-0.5px;}
h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--gold);}
.hero-sub{font-size:15px;font-weight:300;color:var(--grey);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:38px;max-width:420px;}
.btn-row{display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:40px;}
.btn-dark{background:var(--charcoal);color:var(--cream);padding:13px 30px;border-radius:2px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;border:1.5px solid var(--charcoal);transition:all 0.2s;}
.btn-dark:hover{background:var(--gold);border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--charcoal);}
.btn-outline{background:transparent;color:var(--charcoal);padding:13px 30px;border-radius:2px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;border:1.5px solid var(--charcoal);transition:all 0.2s;}
.btn-outline:hover{border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--gold);}
.trust-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.trust-row span{font-size:12px;color:var(--grey);font-weight:300;}
.trust-sep{width:3px;height:3px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);}
.hero-right{animation:fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.12s both;}
.hero-card{background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;padding:40px 36px;position:relative;}
.hero-card::before{content:"";position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:var(--gold);border-radius:3px 3px 0 0;}
.hero-card-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:20px;}
.hero-price-row{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:4px;margin-bottom:6px;}
.hero-price{font-family:"Cormorant Garamond",serif;font-size:50px;font-weight:500;color:var(--charcoal);line-height:1;}
.hero-price-unit{font-size:17px;color:var(--grey);font-weight:300;margin-bottom:7px;}
.hero-price-sub{font-size:13px;color:var(--grey);font-weight:300;margin-bottom:28px;line-height:1.5;}
.hero-divider{height:1px;background:var(--border);margin-bottom:24px;}
.hero-list{list-style:none;}
.hero-list li{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;font-size:13px;color:var(--charcoal);font-weight:400;padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);line-height:1.4;}
.hero-list li:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.h-dot{width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);flex-shrink:0;}
.ticker{background:var(--charcoal);padding:13px 0;overflow:hidden;}
.ticker-track{display:flex;width:max-content;animation:ticker 30s linear infinite;}
.ticker-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;padding:0 28px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(250,247,242,0.4);white-space:nowrap;}
.t-dot{width:3px;height:3px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);opacity:0.5;}
@keyframes ticker{from{transform:translateX(0);}to{transform:translateX(-50%);}}
section{padding:96px 64px;}
.inner{max-width:1160px;margin:0 auto;}
.sec-label{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:3.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:16px;}
.sec-label::before{content:"";width:20px;height:1px;background:var(--gold);}
h2{font-family:"Cormorant Garamond",serif;font-size:40px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.15;color:var(--charcoal);margin-bottom:14px;}
.sec-sub{font-size:15px;font-weight:300;color:var(--grey);line-height:1.75;max-width:500px;}
.problem{background:var(--white);}
.problem-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:var(--border);margin-top:52px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden;}
.p-card{background:var(--cream);padding:36px 30px;transition:background 0.2s;}
.p-card:hover{background:var(--white);}
.p-bar{width:24px;height:2px;background:var(--gold);margin-bottom:20px;}
.p-title{font-family:"Cormorant Garamond",serif;font-size:21px;font-weight:500;color:var(--charcoal);margin-bottom:10px;}
.p-text{font-size:13px;font-weight:300;color:var(--grey);line-height:1.75;}
.problem-note{margin-top:40px;padding:24px 32px;border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:2px solid var(--gold);border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;}
.problem-note p{font-family:"Cormorant Garamond",serif;font-size:21px;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;color:var(--grey);line-height:1.5;}
.problem-note p strong{color:var(--charcoal);font-style:normal;font-weight:500;}
.services{background:var(--cream);}
.svc-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px;margin-top:48px;}
.svc-card{background:var(--white);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;padding:26px 22px;transition:all 0.2s;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.svc-card::after{content:"";position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:var(--gold);transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:left;transition:transform 0.3s;}
.svc-card:hover::after{transform:scaleX(1);}
.svc-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px var(--shadow);}
.svc-mark{width:28px;height:28px;border:1px solid var(--gold-light);background:var(--gold-pale);border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
.svc-mark svg{width:13px;height:13px;stroke:var(--gold);fill:none;stroke-width:1.5;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}
.svc-title{font-family:"Cormorant Garamond",serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--charcoal);margin-bottom:7px;}
.svc-text{font-size:12px;font-weight:300;color:var(--grey);line-height:1.7;}
.pricing{background:var(--white);}
.pricing-wrap{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px;margin-top:48px;max-width:800px;}
.price-card{border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--cream);}
.price-card.feat{background:var(--white);border-color:var(--gold);}
.price-top{padding:30px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
.price-card.feat .price-top{background:var(--charcoal);border-bottom-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);}
.price-tag{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:10px;}
.price-name{font-family:"Cormorant Garamond",serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:500;color:var(--charcoal);margin-bottom:14px;}
.price-card.feat .price-name{color:var(--cream);}
.price-num{font-family:"Cormorant Garamond",serif;font-size:42px;font-weight:600;color:var(--charcoal);line-height:1;}
.price-card.feat .price-num{color:var(--gold);}
.price-mo{font-size:12px;color:var(--grey);margin-top:4px;}
.price-card.feat .price-mo{color:rgba(250,247,242,0.35);}
.price-hrs{display:inline-block;margin-top:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);background:rgba(201,169,110,0.1);padding:3px 9px;border-radius:2px;}
.price-body{padding:26px 30px;}
.price-list{list-style:none;}
.price-list li{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);font-size:13px;font-weight:300;color:var(--charcoal);line-height:1.5;}
.price-list li:last-child{border-bottom:none;}
.price-list li::before{content:"";width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:6px;}
.price-btn{display:block;margin:4px 30px 26px;text-align:center;padding:12px;border-radius:2px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;border:1.5px solid var(--charcoal);color:var(--charcoal);transition:all 0.2s;}
.price-btn:hover{background:var(--charcoal);color:var(--cream);}
.price-card.feat .price-btn{background:var(--gold);border-color:var(--gold);color:var(--charcoal);}
.price-card.feat .price-btn:hover{background:var(--charcoal);border-color:var(--charcoal);color:var(--cream);}
.price-note{margin-top:24px;max-width:800px;padding:22px 28px;background:var(--cream);border:1px solid var(--border);border-left:2px solid var(--gold);border-radius:0 3px 3px 0;}
.price-note p{font-size:14px;font-weight:300;color:var(--grey);line-height:1.75;}
.price-note strong{color:var(--charcoal);font-weight:600;}
.about{background:var(--cream);}
.about-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:80px;align-items:center;margin-top:48px;}
.about-visual{position:relative;}
.about-box{width:100%;aspect-ratio:4/5;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.about-box img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;display:block;}
.about-badge{position:absolute;bottom:-18px;right:-18px;width:76px;height:76px;background:var(--gold-pale);border:1px solid var(--gold-light);border-radius:2px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;}
.about-badge span{font-size:9px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);line-height:1.4;}
.about-text p{font-size:15px;font-weight:300;color:var(--grey);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:18px;}
.about-text p:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}
.about-text strong{color:var(--charcoal);font-weight:500;}
.founder{background:var(--white);}
.founder-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:280px 1fr;gap:64px;align-items:start;margin-top:48px;max-width:860px;}
.founder-img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:3/4;border-radius:3px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.founder-img img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center top;display:block;}
.f-bar{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;background:var(--charcoal);padding:14px 18px;}
.f-name{font-family:"Cormorant Garamond",serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;color:var(--cream);}
.f-title{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-top:2px;}
.f-quote{font-family:"Cormorant Garamond",serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;color:var(--charcoal);line-height:1.45;margin-bottom:24px;padding-left:18px;border-left:2px solid var(--gold);}
.f-bio{font-size:14px;font-weight:300;color:var(--grey);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:14px;}
.f-tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin-top:22px;}
.f-tag{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--charcoal);background:var(--cream);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:5px 12px;border-radius:2px;}
.faq{background:var(--cream);}
.faq-wrap{margin-top:44px;max-width:700px;}
.faq-item{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
.faq-q{width:100%;background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;padding:20px 0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:20px;text-align:left;}
.faq-q-text{font-family:"Cormorant Garamond",serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:500;color:var(--charcoal);line-height:1.3;}
.faq-icon{width:24px;height:24px;flex-shrink:0;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all 0.3s;}
.faq-icon svg{width:10px;height:10px;stroke:var(--gold);fill:none;stroke-width:2;stroke-linecap:round;transition:transform 0.3s;}
.faq-item.open .faq-icon{background:var(--gold);border-color:var(--gold);}
.faq-item.open .faq-icon svg{stroke:var(--white);transform:rotate(45deg);}
.faq-ans{max-height:0;overflow:hidden;transition:max-height 0.4s ease;}
.faq-ans-inner{padding:0 0 18px;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;color:var(--grey);line-height:1.8;}
.contact{background:var(--charcoal);padding:96px 64px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;}
.c-ring-1{position:absolute;right:-60px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);width:300px;height:300px;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.09);pointer-events:none;}
.c-ring-2{position:absolute;right:20px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);width:180px;height:180px;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.05);pointer-events:none;}
.contact-inner{max-width:600px;position:relative;z-index:2;}
.c-label{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:3.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:18px;}
.c-label::before{content:"";width:20px;height:1px;background:var(--gold);}
.contact h2{font-family:"Cormorant Garamond",serif;font-size:42px;font-weight:500;color:var(--cream);line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:16px;}
.contact-sub{font-size:15px;font-weight:300;color:rgba(250,247,242,0.45);line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:36px;max-width:460px;}
.contact-btns{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:40px;}
.btn-gold{background:var(--gold);color:var(--charcoal);padding:13px 30px;border-radius:2px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;border:1.5px solid var(--gold);transition:all 0.2s;}
.btn-gold:hover{background:transparent;color:var(--gold);}
.btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--cream);padding:13px 30px;border-radius:2px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;border:1.5px solid rgba(250,247,242,0.22);transition:all 0.2s;}
.btn-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--cream);}
.contact-details{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.contact-details a{font-size:13px;color:rgba(250,247,242,0.38);text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.2s;}
.contact-details a:hover{color:var(--gold);}
.cd{width:3px;height:3px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(250,247,242,0.18);}
.contact-note{margin-top:36px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid rgba(250,247,242,0.07);font-size:12px;font-style:italic;color:rgba(250,247,242,0.22);}
footer{background:#131210;padding:26px 64px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;}
.footer-logo{font-family:"Cormorant Garamond",serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;color:rgba(250,247,242,0.35);}
.footer-logo span{color:var(--gold);}
.footer-links{display:flex;gap:24px;list-style:none;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.footer-links a{font-size:11px;color:rgba(250,247,242,0.22);text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.5px;transition:color 0.2s;}
.footer-links a:hover{color:var(--gold);}
.footer-copy{font-size:11px;color:rgba(250,247,242,0.18);}
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);transition:opacity 0.65s ease,transform 0.65s ease;}
.reveal.visible{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
.d1{transition-delay:0.1s;}.d2{transition-delay:0.2s;}
@media(max-width:900px){
  nav{padding:0 24px;}.nav-links{display:none;}
  .hero{padding:90px 24px 60px;}
  .hero-content{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:40px;}
  h1{font-size:38px;}.hero-right{display:none;}
  section{padding:64px 24px;}
  .problem-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .svc-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
  .pricing-wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .about-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}.about-visual{display:none;}
  .founder-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}.founder-img{display:none;}
  .contact{padding:64px 24px;}
  footer{padding:24px;flex-direction:column;text-align:center;}
  h2{font-size:32px;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav id="nav">
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">Her Desk <span>Co.</span></a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
    <li><a href="#pricing">Pricing</a></li>
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#founder">Founder</a></li>
    <li><a href="#faq">FAQ</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://calendly.com/jade-adminsupport/30min" target="_blank" class="nav-cta">Book a Call</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>
<section class="hero" id="home">
  <div class="hero-ring-1"></div><div class="hero-ring-2"></div>
  <div class="hero-dot-a"></div><div class="hero-dot-b"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-left">
      <div class="eyebrow">Remote Back-Office Support</div>
      <h1>Your clinic deserves a back office that actually <em>keeps up.</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Her Desk Co. handles your patient follow-ups, scheduling, invoicing, and admin — remotely, professionally, without the cost of a full-time hire.</p>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <a href="https://calendly.com/jade-adminsupport/30min" target="_blank" class="btn-dark">Book a Free Call</a>
        <a href="#services" class="btn-outline">See How It Works</a>
      </div>
      <div class="trust-row">
        <span>Bilingual Support</span><div class="trust-sep"></div>
        <span>English &amp; French</span><div class="trust-sep"></div>
        <span>Medical Admin Experience</span><div class="trust-sep"></div>
        <span>Based in Canada</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-right">
      <div class="hero-card">
        <div class="hero-card-label">Starting At</div>
        <div class="hero-price-row">
          <div class="hero-price">$1,500</div>
          <div class="hero-price-unit">/mo</div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-price-sub">vs. $45,000&#8211;$60,000/year for a full-time admin hire</div>
        <div class="hero-divider"></div>
        <ul class="hero-list">
          <li><div class="h-dot"></div>No benefits or HR overhead</li>
          <li><div class="h-dot"></div>No hiring or training period</li>
          <li><div class="h-dot"></div>Scale up or down any month</li>
          <li><div class="h-dot"></div>Operational within 48 hours</li>
          <li><div class="h-dot"></div>Real medical admin experience</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<div class="ticker">
  <div class="ticker-track">
    <div class="ticker-item">Patient Follow-Ups<div class="t-dot"></div></div>
