      <div class="svc-card reveal d1"><div class="svc-mark"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="6"/><polyline points="8,4 8,8 11,10"/></svg></div><div class="svc-title">Patient Follow-Ups</div><p class="svc-text">Every patient hears back. No one falls through the cracks.</p></div>
      <div class="svc-card reveal d2"><div class="svc-mark"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><rect x="2" y="1" width="12" height="14" rx="1"/><line x1="5" y1="5" x2="11" y2="5"/><line x1="5" y1="8" x2="11" y2="8"/><line x1="5" y1="11" x2="8" y2="11"/></svg></div><div class="svc-title">Invoicing &amp; Tracking</div><p class="svc-text">Invoices go out on time. Outstanding balances followed up consistently.</p></div>
