      <div class="svc-card reveal d1"><div class="svc-mark"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><rect x="1" y="3" width="14" height="10" rx="1"/><polyline points="1,3 8,9 15,3"/></svg></div><div class="svc-title">Email &amp; Calendar Management</div><p class="svc-text">Your inbox and calendar organized, responded to, under control.</p></div>
      <div class="svc-card reveal d2"><div class="svc-mark"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="6"/><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="2"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="10" x2="8" y2="14"/><line x1="2" y1="8" x2="6" y2="8"/><line x1="10" y1="8" x2="14" y2="8"/></svg></div><div class="svc-title">CRM &amp; System Updates</div><p class="svc-text">Jane App, Mindbody, and other platforms kept current and accurate.</p></div>
