<section class="about reveal" id="about">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="sec-label">Our Story</div>
    <h2>Built by a woman who saw<br>the gap firsthand.</h2>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-visual reveal">
        <div class="about-box">
          <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Her Desk Co."/>
        </div>
        <div class="about-badge"><span>Women<br>Owned</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-text reveal d1">
        <p>Her Desk Co. was founded on a simple observation: <strong>the most overwhelmed person in a growing aesthetic clinic is almost always the owner.</strong></p>
        <p>They're performing treatments, managing staff, marketing their business &#8212; and somewhere in between, trying to keep up with everything the back office demands.</p>
        <p>We are a <strong>women-owned remote administrative support agency</strong> built specifically for medical aesthetic clinics and medspas. We build systems, document processes, and become the back office your clinic needs to grow.</p>
        <p>We work with a small number of clinics at a time &#8212; intentionally &#8212; so every client gets real attention and real results.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="founder reveal" id="founder">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="sec-label">Meet the Founder</div>
    <div class="founder-grid">
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="founder-img">
          <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Jade Rancourt"/>
          <div class="f-bar">
            <div class="f-name">Jade Rancourt</div>
            <div class="f-title">Founder &amp; Lead Administrator</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal d1">
        <blockquote class="f-quote">"When you work with Her Desk Co., nothing falls through the cracks. Ever."</blockquote>
        <p class="f-bio">I started Her Desk Co. because I've seen firsthand what happens when a clinic's back office can't keep up with its growth. Patients slip. Revenue is left on the table. The owner ends up doing work that shouldn't be on their plate.</p>
        <p class="f-bio">I bring real medical administrative experience, a structured approach, and genuine care for every clinic I work with.</p>
        <div class="f-tags">
          <span class="f-tag">Medical Admin Background</span>
          <span class="f-tag">Bilingual FR / EN</span>
          <span class="f-tag">Based in Canada</span>
          <span class="f-tag">Jane App</span>
          <span class="f-tag">Women-Owned</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="faq reveal" id="faq">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="sec-label">FAQ</div>
    <h2>Questions we get asked.</h2>
    <div class="faq-wrap">
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">Do I need to sign a long-term contract?</span><span class="faq-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 10 10"><line x1="5" y1="1" x2="5" y2="9"/><line x1="1" y1="5" x2="9" y2="5"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">No. Month to month. Scale up, scale down, or cancel with 30 days notice. No lock-ins, no penalties.</div></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">What software do you work with?</span><span class="faq-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 10 10"><line x1="5" y1="1" x2="5" y2="9"/><line x1="1" y1="5" x2="9" y2="5"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Jane App, Mindbody, Google Workspace, HubSpot, Wave, and more. If you use something different, we learn it quickly and are fully operational within the first two weeks.</div></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">How do I know what's being done each month?</span><span class="faq-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 10 10"><line x1="5" y1="1" x2="5" y2="9"/><line x1="1" y1="5" x2="9" y2="5"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Every Friday you receive a weekly summary of everything completed. Growth Plan clients also receive a bi-weekly check-in call.</div></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">How quickly can you start?</span><span class="faq-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 10 10"><line x1="5" y1="1" x2="5" y2="9"/><line x1="1" y1="5" x2="9" y2="5"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Within 48&#8211;72 hours of signing. A short onboarding call, access to your systems, and we get started. No delays.</div></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">Is my patient information secure?</span><span class="faq-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 10 10"><line x1="5" y1="1" x2="5" y2="9"/><line x1="1" y1="5" x2="9" y2="5"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Yes. All patient and clinic information is treated with full confidentiality. We are happy to sign an NDA before onboarding begins.</div></div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q"><span class="faq-q-text">Are you bilingual?</span><span class="faq-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 10 10"><line x1="5" y1="1" x2="5" y2="9"/><line x1="1" y1="5" x2="9" y2="5"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-ans"><div class="faq-ans-inner">Yes &#8212; full support in English and French, making us a strong fit for clinics serving bilingual or francophone patients across Canada.</div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
